==English==

===Etymology===
From {{etyl|la}} {{term|stamina|stāmina|lang=la}}, plural of {{term|stamen|stāmen}}.

===Pronunciation===
* {{a|UK}} {{IPA|/ˈstamɪnə/}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun|-}}

# {{uncountable|now considered singular}} The energy and strength for continuing to do something over a long period of time ; power of sustained exertion, or resistance to hardship, illness etc.
# {{botany|rare}} {{plural of|[[stamen]]}}
# {{context|obsolete|as plural}} The basic elements of a thing ; rudimentary structures or qualities.

